以下的练习是从IC 网上练习本转用的。The following exercises are adapted from the IC Webapp Workbook L14-2 Grammar and Writing section, Q4, Q6, and Q9

Grammar and Writing 4/D.

Your friend is studying fashion marketing and would like to interview you for an assignment. Answer the following questions based on what you are wearing today. Be sure to use the 是。。。的 structure in your answers! 

  - 你的衣服是什么时候买的？
  - 你的衣服是在哪儿买的？
  - 你的衣服是谁买的？
  - 你的衣服是花多少钱买的？

 

Grammar and Writing 6/F. 

Describe this dog in 4-5 sentences . Please comment on the points below.  

    好看/不好看/可爱/不可爱
    毛 (fur), 脚，眼睛，耳朵，鼻子
    大/小 ， 胖/瘦 
     your thoughts about the dog's disposition or state of mind - 它好像 。。。 

doubled adjectives can express appreciation of a trait:  它的尾巴长长的/它有长长的尾巴(wěiba tail)

比较 bǐjiào = relatively f.ex. 他的尾巴比较长
cute little puppy with big, black eyes, brown fur, white snout, white belly, white paws, etc.

 

 

Grammar and Writing 9/I 

你要为你的好朋友开生日派对(pàiduì party)。请你写下来你的计划(jìhuà plans)  ：

（每一个问题写一句 One sentence per question)  

    在哪儿开?
    要请谁 ?
    几点到几点 ?
    要做什么？ (first, next, after that...) 
    什么样的蛋糕 ？
    别人可以带 ....
    要不要送礼物 ？什么样的礼物？  
    要是你不能走路去。。。
    是不是惊喜(jīngxǐ surprise )派对 ？
